WEBVTT

00:00:56.880 --> 00:01:00.696
I spent three years
talking to girls ages 15 to 20

00:01:00.720 --> 00:01:03.656
about their attitudes
and experience of sex.

00:01:03.680 --> 00:01:05.096
And what I found was

00:01:05.120 --> 00:01:09.416
that while young women may feel
entitled to engage in sexual behavior,

00:01:09.440 --> 00:01:12.520
they don't necessarily
feel entitled to enjoy it.

00:01:13.240 --> 00:01:15.376
Take this sophomore
at the Ivy League college

00:01:15.400 --> 00:01:16.616
who told me,

00:01:16.640 --> 00:01:19.896
"I come from a long line
of smart, strong women.

00:01:19.920 --> 00:01:22.136
My grandmother was a firecracker,

00:01:22.160 --> 00:01:24.016
my mom is a professional,

00:01:24.040 --> 00:01:27.400
my sister and I are loud,
and that's our form of feminine power."

